item.description:
- this collection conatins all about chat


- like send **messages** and **Rooms** events
- all of apis need the user identifier to make the oprations
- {{user1}} and {{usr2}} is just the users identifiers that you alreay send over theregister proccess
- we have 4 type of chats
- 1\. single (s) direct chat
- 2\. group chat (g)
- 3\. broadcast chat (b) lick whatsapp broadcast
- 4\. order chat (o) this will be use for if you want to create chat between buyer and seller for spicfic product


some of key short cut i have mad to reduce the data send and recive

```
// userId
uId: string;
//roomId
rId: string;
//lastSeenMessageId
lSMId: string;
//roomType
rT: RoomType;
//title
t: string;
//translatedTo
tTo?: string,
//title English
tEn: string;
//nick title
nTitle: string;
//image
img: string,
// isDeleted
isD: boolean,
// isArchived
isA: boolean,
// isMuted
isM: boolean,
//peerID
pId?: string,

```

for message we have this

```
//senderId
sId: string,
//senderIdentifier
sIdentifier: string,
//senderName
sName: string,
//senderImageThumb
sImg: string,
//platform (os)
plm: string,
//room id
rId: string;
//message content
c: string;
//message type
mT: MessageType,
//message attachment
msgAtt: object,
//attached link info
linkAtt: object,
//replied to message
rTo: IMessage,
//seen at
sAt: Date,
//delivered at
dAt: Date,
///deleted from all at
dltAt: Date,
//parent broadcast message id
pBId: string,
//who star
stars: string[],
isEncrypted: boolean,
//deleted from (only me)
dF: string[],
//local Id
lId: string,
//forward from message id
forId?: string,
```
